en.title: What Animal Nature Do I Have?
en.description: Though we may seem similar on the surface, your unconscious mind definitely possesses an 'animal nature'. Through this test, discover what animal represents your inner nature.
en.seoKeywords: animal test, animal psychology, animal personality

questions.question: What type are you in gatherings?
options: Become a leader and guide everyone.
Stay quiet then match the atmosphere.
Talk to everyone and become friends.
Gatherings are hard. Want to go home.

questions.question: Your reaction when stressed?
options: Exercise or go out and be active.
Want to be alone and enter silent mode.
Act calm as usual but feel uncomfortable inside.

questions.question: If you describe yourself in one word?
When a friend shares their worries, you:
options: "Wow really? That's ridiculous!" Express emotions together
"Why did you feel that way?" Analyze the cause

questions.question: In crowded places, you:
options: Feel tired but watch others' reactions.
Adapt well but don't want to stay long
Lead the atmosphere and take charge.
Observe people and find interesting points

questions.question: What kind of child were you?
options: Leader type who led friends around
Preferred playing alone over standing out

questions.question: What type of person do you dislike?
options: People who can't read the room
People who stand out and ruin the mood

questions.question: In moments of decision, you:
options: Analyze and compare pros/cons before deciding
Listen to others' thoughts and decide

- Prefers alone time

Good at social skills and sensitive to danger detection.
